name: DINO MUNCH (OUTCASTgames)
description:
It's eat or be eaten on the chaotic Island of Dino Munch! Eat the dinos that are smaller than you, and avoid the Dinos that are larger than you or you might be eaten yourself!

Special thanks to Spencer Glenn for the bangin' soundtrack!

Check out his other music here:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCYPYrwquCgSPkJLX5BmQLw
